content:
It is difficult to determine which wrestler has won the most matches as it depends on the time period and weight class considered. However, some of the most successful wrestlers in recent history include:

* Cael Sanderson, American wrestler and former Olympic gold medalist
* Abdulrashid Sadulaev, Russian wrestler and Olympic gold medalist
* Jordan Burroughs, American wrestler and Olympic gold medalist
* Henry Cejudo, American mixed martial artist and former Olympic wrestler
* Kyle Dake, American wrestler and four-time NCAA champion

These wrestlers have accomplished a great deal in their careers, winning numerous national and international championships, as well as setting records for their success on the mat.
